      "title": "Young woman died and her sister injured in train mishap in Wellawatta",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 20-year old woman had died and her sister was injured after they were hit by a moving train in Wellawatta last night, police said.",
        "The Wellawatta Police initiated investigation after the two young women were hit by a Colombo-bound train from Aluthgama near the Police Life Saving Unit.",
        "Police said both the women were admitted to the Colombo South Teaching Hospital and one of them succumbed to her injuries."
